data.description: East Rowan Schools!  Come see this 3 BR 2 bath manufactured home sitting on .82 acres and see all that it has to offer!  Walk into a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and laminate flooring.  Kitchen and dining area are open to main living - perfect for entertaining.  Kitchen offers sit in bar area - all appliances convey!  Large primary bedroom offers walk in closet and spacious bath w/double vanity, soaking tub and stand alone shower.  2 more BRs offer great space as well!  Laundry is separate area off kitchen.  Rear yard is fenced and offers multiple storage buildings and outdoor fireplace.  Book your showing today - make this your home tomorrow!!
